{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "苏方 第5话 永久传承的志向",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "要开始了哦！三、二、一……点火！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "孩子1",
            "context": "哇！好厉害！\\n这就是仙花焰吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "孩子2",
            "context": "嗯！好漂亮！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "苏方？\\n你怎么一脸难以言喻的表情？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "啊！难道是因为……\\n刚才放的仙花焰不够成功？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "纳姆，你这样对苏方很没礼貌哦。\\n他这种水平的工匠怎么会……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不不，没准……\\n正因为是工匠？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "工匠也许会执着于\\n外行所不了解的细节。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "那个……各位，我没事！\\n仙花焰还是一如既往的质量！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是吗，不愧是苏方啊。\\n那你怎么露出那种表情？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "因为……看到这些孩子们，\\n我就想起了之前那个男孩。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "之前……啊，难道就是\\n被魔兽袭击的村子的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "嗯……\\n那个失去了父母的男孩。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "虽然他当时很消沉，\\n但看到我的仙花焰后恢复了精神……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "我很想知道\\n那之后他怎么样了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊……\\n要是能振作起来就好了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好，那我们就去村里\\n看看他的情况吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "啊……\\n那个人，难道是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "你又来了啊，苏方！\\n不……师父！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01",
                "100003_01",
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "众人",
            "context": "师、师父！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "厉害！你什么时候\\n都有弟子了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "不……不不！不是的！\\n我没有收过弟子……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "喔，太好了！\\n那我就是开门大弟子了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "不过，放心吧！\\n我会继承师父的仙花焰技术！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "继承仙花焰的技术……\\n不行！那绝对不行！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "如果错误使用仙花焰会很危险！\\n我不能随随便便地就教给你！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "如果把它交到只想学技术\\n用来做坏事的人手里……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "做坏事！？你、你别小看我！\\n我才不是那种人！我是认真的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你们都冷静点。\\n我们来整理一下来龙去脉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "首先，你想当苏方的弟子，\\n进行仙花焰工匠的修行对吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "是的！我已经做好艰苦修行的觉悟了！\\n一开始我就说了吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "是、是吗！？不，那个……\\n我不记得你说过……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "那我现在再说一遍！拜托你了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "收我当弟子吧！我也想\\n用仙花焰赋予人们生的希望！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "诶……\\n赋予人们生的希望？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "是啊！因为师父\\n你让我看到的仙花焰，太让人感动……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "怎么说呢，就是……\\n让我想要继续活下去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "所以，如果别人\\n也变得像我那样……\\n我想用仙花焰让他振作起来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样啊，很远大的志向呢。\\n我说……苏方？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "诶？那、那个，唔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "嗯……我觉得是很远大的志向。\\n为了他人的笑容\\n而放仙花焰……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "对仙花焰工匠来说最重要的东西，\\n这孩子一开始就懂了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，这孩子应该没问题吧，\\n你不用担心……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "也许吧……\\n好，我也决定了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "咦！？那、那就是说……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "嗯，我愿意收你为弟子。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "太好啦！\\n谢谢师父！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "现在高兴还太早。\\n今后每天都有严苛的修行在等着你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "噢！求之不得！\\n那么，我要怎么做？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "什么都不做……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "明白了！什么都不做……\\n咦？为、为什么！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "咦，我没有说过吗。\\n修行首先要从内心开始。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "在我认可之前，\\n是不会让你碰仙花焰的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "没问题吧？唔……\\n说起来，你的名字是？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯文",
            "context": "我叫凯文！要好好记住哦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯文",
            "context": "看着吧，师父！\\n我一定会尽快让你认可我！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "两人就这样成为了师徒。\\n为庆祝新的开始，\\n苏方放了仙花焰。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯文",
            "context": "好棒！还有能变色的仙花焰吗！\\n到底是什么原理……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哈哈，凯文已经被仙花焰迷住了。\\n你的弟子真有热情啊，苏方。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "尤蒂尔……\\n我能成为一位合格的师父吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "虽然我嘴上说着什么“修行要从\\n内心开始”这种冠冕堂皇的话，\\n但那不过是从我师父那里现学现卖……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是吗……\\n不过我觉得现学现卖也挺好的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "咦？那是什么意思……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那就意味着，师父对你的教诲……\\n还有志向都由你继承下来了对吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以，接下来就由你\\n再传授给弟子不就行了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "志向……我从师父那里……\\n从父亲那里……继承的教诲……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "谢谢你，尤蒂尔……\\n我似乎已经明白……\\n什么才是自己的使命了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "我要把代代相传的志向\\n传递给下一代。并且……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110314_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "苏方",
            "context": "由我和弟子一起完成！我们要让仙花焰\\n绽放在整片大陆的夜空中！　",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}